{"tid":1695730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突破華生】工會抗爭方程式！冇得輸嘅閃擊戰術 先禮後兵2.0","createTime":"2019-11-05T21:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:12:02.000Z","uid":53610,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4b04766b719804d35121f0fd7d38bfdee15030ed","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T21:59:47.000Z","msg":"事源是咁的，話說依排係組織工會的季節，好多工會新生萌芽，紛紛冒起，當然仲遠遠唔夠啦，我哋目標係每個業界都組成至少一個大工會，為實現最終目標－無了期攬炒罷工而鋪路<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，運輸業界係工會計劃中的關鍵之一，重要性同街亭有得揮，而就係不久之前新生的巴士工會－<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴士業職工會聯盟</span></span>就急不及待打算搞返個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">《全城口罩日》</span></span>，想話喺巴士派下口罩預防流感咁啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勢估唔到個頭炮未打響就俾人嚟咗個下馬威，阿<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">新巴</span></span>話正值敏感時期，就唔撚派得口罩喎，唔知有冇警婦個水炮閪咁敏感呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/189574754981356/posts/483484782257017?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F189574754981356%2Fposts%2F483484782257017%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=dc35c0e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/189574754981356/posts/483484782257017?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nSo？<br />\n正常人個第一反應都會想提早開佢年先啦，點知嬲緊嗰陣忽然靈機一動，俾我諗到條絕世好橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新生工會有活動，紅資藍企俾壓力想玩串個 party其實都幾正路，不過唔知點解我就從中感受到一股熟悉的感覺<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先禮後兵</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理&rarr;死線&rarr;升級&rarr;勇武</span><br />\n<br />\n還記得抗爭之初，我都有份整合依條抗爭方程式，條公式包含著先禮後兵的精髓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先以和平示威的手段表達訴求，拎咗個高地先講，再迫政府喺死線之前回應，唔回應就可以名正言順咁升級勇武<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然之後除住政府把心一橫，決意鎮壓到底，依條方程式已經慢慢淡出舞台，但箇中原理仲係頗具參考價值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">所以呢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底依條方程式又同工會活動有咩關係呢？<br />\n<br />\n以今次巴士界工會為例，溫和咁派口罩就好比當初的和理行動，紅資藍企的壓迫就同港府拒絕回應大遊行一樣落人口實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到依一步，我哋已經可以同五個月前對特衰政府一樣，高舉名正言順的旗幟聲討依啲商家企業，並且付諸行動，道理喺我哋依邊，我哋係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「先受壓，再反抗」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上由一開始依啲公司就得兩個選擇<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放任</span></span>－由得工會組織和理活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">施壓</span></span>－同時承認自己藍企身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔理邊面，贏的都係我哋，欺壓工會的紅資藍企以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]黑店[/black]</span></strong>規格視之<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">裝修</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">罷買</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記著新的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工會抗爭方程式</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />工會和理活動&rarr;受壓<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">&rarr;標記藍企&rarr;裝修罷買</div></span><br />\n此一方程底下，藍企無所遁形，一係默認新生工會的發展，一係賭下自己會唔會變成下個美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前棋為誘餌，後棋為殺著，不論前棋係被食定係主動移開半步，後棋都可以直取<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅心</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n喺象棋界稱之為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">閃擊戰術</span>！</span>"},{"pid":"80d2a910fbb3ec61acb846103b121878f194baab","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T22:03:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要的係<br />\n我哋有義務去保護所有<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">新生的工會</span></span>"},{"pid":"f23ae39b51df45512670647c7a43cdf07cd9ef1e","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T22:13:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星星之火</span>已經點燃<br />\n守護好我哋的火種<br />\n好快會變成十級大火</span>"},{"pid":"ebf788382e57fe83759d399c96ea6120fa35e819","tid":1695730,"uid":137371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T22:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1706a906fcd8cdac73b04c84a2db24c932a1f2fd","tid":1695730,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:55:30.000Z","msg":"11月9日：7區開花！香港人反抗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689356\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bc42e8a49d96123ea550b3ba7cd23e558674a00","tid":1695730,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83fac824670cf2d4f5bf955392ccfbb3d4cd744d","tid":1695730,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:03:31.000Z","msg":"推呢個 其實先禮後兵仲可以同啲企業同文宣講 依家係政府唔回應訴求 先要搞工會去罷工 <br />\n<br />\n唔係我地搞鳩你 怪就怪政府<br />\n等商家都對政府施壓"},{"pid":"e13e18e452c36fc69ec077749e4895a9973905c9","tid":1695730,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18186586961c036818ccab94df0a8418003500c","tid":1695730,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc436f2b2ad920230c1779aedafc99509a4f1354","tid":1695730,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"香港人要有工會"},{"pid":"7d417e25c5d9e8c736832267ab9011d261e3ce61","tid":1695730,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:32:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"626ac5c73b83ba726a6bc9861047ec7cb210df70","tid":1695730,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:41:23.000Z","msg":"曱甴王習曱甴"},{"pid":"2ae70ca25f38a3b943ea13e04886d5cb4aa32aaf","tid":1695730,"uid":18223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0af296c42f62b7922691a878595c9631b557f864","tid":1695730,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:47:38.000Z","msg":"推實事巴打"},{"pid":"c64bb7b0a0222974d900179f3fa9e05ba3f35f22","tid":1695730,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ea9d87d386a8ce3571b00fed8ceae58a9ee7ed","tid":1695730,"uid":266643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2161592ae15a487fd5ac0f8ad20e903d869e0b0c","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"919fd0186265f412775798bd1dfde2d726371724","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83fac824670cf2d4f5bf955392ccfbb3d4cd744d","tid":1695730,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:03:31.000Z","msg":"推呢個 其實先禮後兵仲可以同啲企業同文宣講 依家係政府唔回應訴求 先要搞工會去罷工 <br />\n<br />\n唔係我地搞鳩你 怪就怪政府<br />\n等商家都對政府施壓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"政府就話可以鎮壓啫<br />\n你做香港人生意的商家可以點拆先禮後兵依招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依條方程式的應用層面比我哋想像中要廣得多"},{"pid":"8d5f42c87449da2eb5b038bcdb5a94aa50111eba","tid":1695730,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435f2e26585955c259ef4bf7325e4c7a045451ab","tid":1695730,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf17b49a803ac8dfc1f5de8f68ae30d9b2145c8","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"fe8e16ce2361e936a61f89e7ac4153ed20fddc24","tid":1695730,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb7e0fdee72be816e811181e